  "title": "Laundry Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Collection of laundry items from customers</li>\n  <li>Detail check &amp; tagging of the garments/linen for defects, discolour, missing accessories, etc</li>\n  <li>Follow the job process as stated in the Laundry Procedures</li>\n  <li>Carry out daily counter operation and duties</li>\n  <li>Manage and ensure the cleanliness of counter</li>\n  <li>Ensure all payments received are accurate and tally with the daily cashier report</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of English in both verbal and written communication.</li>\n  <li>Computer Savvy</li>\n  <li>Confident with a pleasant disposition and well-groomed</li>\n  <li>A friendly personality and meticulous working attitude.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Mon-Fri (11am-8.45pm;1-hr lunch break)</li>\n  <li>Meals provided</li>\n  <li>Work Location at Bayfront</li>\n</ul>",
